Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.48,0:00:04.90,zhengwenscn,NTP,0,0,0,,要对圣母玛利亚 保·密·哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.48,0:00:11.57,zhengwenscn,NTP,0,0,0,,真可口呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.94,0:00:13.15,zhengwenscn,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了～
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.62,0:00:19.41,zhengwenscn,NTP,0,0,0,,太夸张了呢  佑巳
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.24,0:00:21.16,zhengwenscn,NTP,0,0,0,,实在过意不去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.00,0:00:27.38,zhengwenscn,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然想给姐姐打个电话为今天的事致谢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.04,0:00:29.92,zhengwenscn,NTP,0,0,0,,可是却不知道会是哪一位来接听
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.42,0:00:32.21,zhengwenscn,NTP,0,0,0,,真不是那么轻易就能打出去的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.09,0:00:37.80,zhengwenscn,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  我是福泽
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.31,0:00:41.10,zhengwenscn,NTP,0,0,0,,弄错而给挂断了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.14,0:00:44.27,zhengwenscn,NTP,0,0,0,,沉着一点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.52,0:00:49.48,zhengwenscn,NTP,0,0,0,,明天见
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.52,0:00:53.90,zhengwenscn,NTP,0,0,0,,到了明天就能再与最喜欢的姐姐相见
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.57,0:00:58.20,zhengwenscn,NTP,0,0,0,,既然今天是如此愉快的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.78,0:01:01.87,zhengwenscn,NTP,0,0,0,,所以明天也一定会是美好的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.12,0:01:06.50,zhengwenscn,NTP,0,0,0,,那便是我与姐姐的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.05,0:01:13.46,zhengwenscn,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安  姐姐
